ume closes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Okt 2018) 4aAnerkennung. 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aBildungssoziologie. 4aBiografieforschung. 4aBiographical Research. 4aDiscrimination. 4aDiskriminierung. 4aEducation. 4aEducational Research. 4aMigrant Entrepreneurship. 4aMigrantisches Unternehmertum. 4aMigration. 4aPolitics of Acknowledgment. 4aSociology of Education. 4aSociology of Work and Industry. 4aSociology. 4aSoziale Aufwärtsmobilität. 4aSoziologie. 4aStigma. 4aUpward Social Mobility. 4aWork.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839445327zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839445327.jpg  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018